It could be somebody else
at your table, somebody

00:20:18.486 --> 00:20:19.130
else nearby.

00:20:19.130 --> 00:20:20.540
Pair up and I'm
going to give you

00:20:20.540 --> 00:20:22.990
three minutes just to share
with one another what you wrote.

00:20:22.990 --> 00:20:25.115
I'll tell you when a minute
and a half has gone by.

00:20:25.115 --> 00:20:28.203
