00:31:43.016 --> 00:31:44.140
I'm not going to be a poet.

00:31:44.140 --> 00:31:46.480
And so I was studying women's
history with Lyde Sizer.

00:31:46.480 --> 00:31:48.420
And I was studying
writing, but not poetry.

00:31:48.420 --> 00:31:49.210
And I was trying
to figure out what

00:31:49.210 --> 00:31:50.180
